<h3>2 - How to acquire spice ?</h3>
<p>You have to ways to earn spice</p> : <br/><br/>the first and simpler way is, <b><a href='<?php echo URL_MAIN_ABS . $this->rewrite('Customer/index/conquete'); ?>'>CONQUER PLANETS</a></b><br/>
