<h3>3 - What do quests bring me ? ? </h3>
<p>By accomplishing quests,you can earn different thing such as : Objects, SPICE, Servants, Influence and Escorts</p>
<p><b>OBJECTS</b> are meant to help you resolve quests, or to give bonus effects. Click on one to use it.</p>
<p><b>SERVANTS</b>, once assigned to a House, make this House's happiness grow. The more a House is happy, the more its representatives will talk to you</p>
<p><b>INFLUENCE POINTS</b>, once assigned to a House, diminish the quantity of spice needed in each ceremony for this House</p>
<p><b>ESCORTS</b>, once assigned to a House, protect this House from <b>MURDERS</b></p>

<p class='warning'>You must assign escorts,influence and servants to the different Houses</p>
<p>It's in fact rare to receive Influence,servants or escorts already assigned to a particular House. <br/>
